name: colorwheel clear watch
description:
All the hues of the color wheel appear and assign a different mood to every hour of the day. The color spectrum contrasts nicely against the clear, transparent watch face & band.

• Hand assembled and made to order in Toronto
• Water resistant; battery included; Japanese quartz movement
• Material: glossy plastic
• Dimensions: 1.2” (watch face diameter) x 9.5” (band length) x 0.65" (band width)
• 6 months manufacturer’s warranty

name: 1971 Volvo 1800 tote bag
description:
Vintage is the name of the game for this tote bag featuring a retro 70's motif and an uber-cool Volvo 1800.

Use it for grocery shopping instead of wasteful plastic or paper bags and show your support for the planet and our environment. Also great for carrying your books, papers, laptop, iPad, etc. For every tote bag we sell we donate 50% of our profits to the Environmental Defense Fund.

Our quality crafted tote bags are hand sewn in America using durable, yet lightweight, poly poplin fabric. All seams and stress points are double stitched for durability. They are washable, feature original artwork on both sides and a sturdy 1" wide cotton webbing strap for comfortably carrying over your shoulder. Dimensions: 16"h x 16"w.
© dzynwrld
